                            <title
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1651545825692]"
                                jcr:created="{Date}2022-12-31T16:05:26.673-05:00"
                                jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-09-05T16:16:04.327-04:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                jcr:title="Things to know before you apply"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                type="h2"
                                variant="h"/>
                            <text
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:created="{Date}2022-12-31T16:11:35.983-05:00"
                                jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2026-01-07T13:25:23.782-05:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>Consider the following items when submitting your application:&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;b>AbbVie has selected providers to be part of the AbbVie Independent Medical Education (IME) Provider Network. &lt;/b>AbbVie will only consider grant requests submitted by providers who are part of the AbbVie IME Provider Network. Submissions from providers who are&amp;nbsp;&lt;i>&lt;b>not&lt;/b>&lt;/i>&amp;nbsp;part of the AbbVie IME Provider Network will no longer be considered for support.&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;b>Please note:&lt;/b>&amp;nbsp; The AbbVie IME Provider Network does not apply to Independent Patient Education, Fellowships, or Call for Grants.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Your grant must be submitted &lt;b>at&amp;nbsp;least 60 days prior&lt;/b>&amp;nbsp;to the decision requested by date.&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>You have the ability to track your request 24/7.&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Your submission will be evaluated against predetermined criteria and must align with AbbVie’s scientific areas of interest.&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>You will receive email notification from AbbVie if additional information is required.&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>You will receive AbbVie’s decision via email. If approved, the authorized signer will receive required documentation (i.e., Letter of Agreement) electronically.&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Grants must reconcile to the approved budget within 90 days following the grant end date.&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Please reference the IME Outcomes Standardization Playbook for our requirements. This can be found on the AbbVie Grants Portal login page.&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;b>To start your grant request&lt;/b>, go to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://abbvie.envisionpharma.com/ienv_abbvie_grants/visiontracker/portal/login.xhtml?pgm=CME&amp;amp;windowId=bb2&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>grants.abbvie.com&lt;/a>. For more details about the application process, see below:&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <separator
                                cq:styleIds="[1662756409908,1662756756047]"
                                jcr:created="{Date}2022-12-31T16:59:58.942-05:00"
                                jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2022-12-31T16:59:58.942-05:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
